00:00:34.989 --> 00:00:39.760
each grain of rice must be milked individually,
removing all of the milk and nutrients from

00:00:39.760 --> 00:00:44.280
the rice and leaving only a fibrous husk,
which can then be used for many purposes,

00:00:44.280 --> 00:00:49.699
but we'll get to that in a minute. This process
is performed by millions of tiny electromechanical

00:00:49.699 --> 00:00:55.199
machines that break down easily, and cannot
